public interface NameIDType extends org.apache.xmlbeans.XmlString
An XML NameIDType(@urn:oasis:names:tc:SAML:2.0:assertion). This is an atomic type that is a restriction of x0Assertion.oasisNamesTcSAML2.NameIDType.
